{"tid":101514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲清秀女師灌醉男學生後做愛　還拍片留念","createTime":"2017-01-31T01:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T12:16:17.000Z","uid":35468,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60b8fe03836e6cbf57cd05137db7c1834674ee61","tid":101514,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"美國又傳出有年輕女老師與未成年男學生做愛，這次不是兩情相悅，而是有如「泥醉」系列成人片中情節，只是被灌醉的是未成年男孩。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n已婚育有1子的路易絲(Sarah Lewis)現年27歲，相貌清秀，在猶他州佩森市(Payson)的藍德馬克高中(Landmark High School)擔任社會學科老師已有2年半。本月初，路易絲帶了一名17歲的男學生回到自己住處，並與他喝了大量的伏特加(Vodka)及啤酒，男學生被灌醉後，路易絲便誘導他與自己做愛。後來因為兩人做愛的影片外流，事件因而曝光，路易絲已在當地時間上周二(24日)遭到州警逮捕，校方並已將她停職。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體報導，路易絲坦承與男學生「做了一次」，但她堅持影片不是自己拍的，她也不知道是誰拍的。案件下周將繼續審理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170131/1046246/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170131%2F1046246%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3d55bbbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170131/1046246/</a>"},{"pid":"4c2ec2dc54d04ef8b7d0a1eaa95cf1c098dd3dc2","tid":101514,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:54:51.000Z","msg":"相貌清秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b52057b0e6d043ad8ca7c0bf52c90d2bc6a1ba","tid":101514,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"唔係美女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39a6a606ea499afac2ae450f3fa267e5f1c9894","tid":101514,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美女老師好變態"},{"pid":"94d90a4883cc3b354bf1c50c9dc243bbda94bc9a","tid":101514,"uid":49392,